reviews:
[{'author_name': 'Rich Atkins', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103924947602594527133/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/AOh14GhqPNbdhKaMNhFUal1hx7BVUdJhs5QuBFnlpuP9Vg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3', 'rating': 1, 'relative_time_description': 'a month ago', 'text': 'My daughter's purse was stolen out of our shopping cart while we were in the store. When this was discovered, we went to Claire, the store manager. She, intimated that my hysterical daughter should leave the store.

I went back a day later to ask for their video surveillance. Claire said that she would contact the people in California to ask them to provide the footage. A week went by, and no word from Claire.

I called her and asked what had happened with my request. She let me know that the people in California didn't see anything.

When was she going to tell me this? She didn't call or email to tell me this. Was I supposed to magically be made aware?

On the phone with her, I let her know that it would be best to allow the victim to see the footage to identify the person who we know stole her purse (thanks to the people at CVS around the corner where the thief used the credit cards). Claire said that they don't do things like that at Trader Joe's. She said that the person could have escaped camera view entirely by skirting around the registers. I asked if they had any cameras trained on any of the aisles. Claire said that they don't. That's when I pointed out that anyone could steal anything at any time, and as long as that person isn't seen then it would go unnoticed.

She said "sir, we like to believe in the integrity of our customers." I said, "well that guy proved you wrong, didn't he?!"

Another week has gone by and I have not heard from Claire about letting my daughter see the footage from the day that we were robbed. It's quite apparent that she does not care that my daughter's purse was stolen in her store and is not willing to do much to help us.

They sell good food. This store has a manager that doesn't care.', 'time': 1650295424}, {'author_name': 'Drea D', 'author_url': 'https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/106900146412445323009/reviews', 'language': 'en', 'profile_photo_url': 'https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/AATXAJyVFOnA4gpnfQu8GZtEuuHsFXeVT8Kf6ZH0Nuk3=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4', 'rating': 5, 'relative_time_description': 'in the last week', 'text': "Great grocery store chain that sells great food, beauty products and more for great prices!
